instructions: Welcome to the story listening part of the experiment.
As a reminder, you will listen to 12 short stories.
These stories will be divided into 2 blocks of 6 stories.
Before some of the stories, we will ask you to take on the perspective of a job.
Please “simulate” this job while you listen to the story that follows.
If you are assigned a perspective, you will take a quiz on it before starting the story.
Before you begin, we will go over how to use the button box:
In this experiment, you'll use the first three fingers on each hand to do the quizzes and advance through the experiment.
